Hi Kay.  Thanks for the compliment.  :-)  

I&#39;m usually surprised upon playback to discover how much more content there was than 
what I caught during the session.  Particularly with manual radio sweep, where I have a 
tendency to receive longer responses than I get with other methods (except EVP Maker 
and the allophones combo - some of those have been surprisingly long.)

Margaret

